{"tid":2034980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[527士氣] 用最少既代價，換取最大既收穫","createTime":"2020-05-25T14:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T14:54:30.000Z","uid":154486,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5482abc6acdac61dee66693d3c6ff203d48f2243","tid":2034980,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:47:52.000Z","msg":"呢個post唔會好長<br />\n<br />\n大家知道<br />\n香港已經進入大直路<br />\n更深既黑暗即將到來<br />\n<br />\n唔只係527﹐以後出黎希望大家保重、冷靜<br />\n用最少既代價換取最大既收穫<br />\n<br />\n而家打爆多幾多隻落單狗黎出氣<br />\n最終都唔及喚醒香港民族，香港獨立重要<br />\n<br />\n因為假如香港人冇民族意識、獨立意識<br />\n比哂成個政總成個立會佢地任出任入<br />\n都唔會尋求獨立<br />\n<br />\n所以係事成之前<br />\n大家要齊齊整整、平平安安番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">民族自強<br />\n香港獨立<br />\nONE Nation<br />\nONE Hong Kong</div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"be7147733cc18ed3b3f12bb69fe2d61fbe909d1f","tid":2034980,"uid":228878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:48:20.000Z","msg":"［正視聽］527 唔好去港島<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2033757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2033757</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n易散水 較安全 動員能力快 有主導權<br />\n求pin<br />\n<br />\n希望大家一齊用愛與和平感動班親共派議員<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53b2bf065212f003220908dc977d6a71a5ff96c3","tid":2034980,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:48:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中環搞和理非活動點睇？<br />\n中午唱吓歌 叫吓口號 吸引國際留意</span>"},{"pid":"c36f39d75f60c11d6f60ff827bd06fe7f038c9ea","tid":2034980,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53b2bf065212f003220908dc977d6a71a5ff96c3","tid":2034980,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T14:48:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中環搞和理非活動點睇？<br />\n中午唱吓歌 叫吓口號 吸引國際留意</